<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <%- include ../partials/header.ejs %>
    </head>
    <body id="profile">
        <% include ../partials/nav %>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>My Profile</h1>
            <p>Each Harmonize profile has a public name to guarantee anonymity. This name will be visible to all Harmonize users.</p>
            <form method="POST" action="/profile" class="update-public-name">
                <label for="">Public name:</label><br>
                <input type="text" name="public-name" id="publicName" value="<%= user.displayName %>" required>
                <input class="waves-effect waves-light btn" type="submit" value="Update">
            </form>
            <br>
            <br>
            <h5>Delete my profile</h5>
            <p>If youâ€™re done using Harmonize and want to delete your profile, click the button below. Just be aware that <span class="underline">deleting a profile is permanent</span>.</p>
            <a href="/profile" class="waves-effect waves-light btn delete-profile-link">Delete Account</a>
        </div>
        <%- include ../partials/footer.ejs %>
        <% include ../partials/alerts %>
    </body>
</html>